{"code":0,"data":{"cancelMargin":1,"claimSwitch":2,"content":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Regras do Servi&ccedil;o de Garantia B&aacute;sica</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">1. Regras de Garantia</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(1) Garantia:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Este site adere ao servi&ccedil;o de garantia terceirizada \"NO Wallet&rdquo;. Em caso de disputas que atendam aos crit&eacute;rios, voc&ecirc; pode solicitar uma indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #999999; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(2) Aten&ccedil;&atilde;o: </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; o &uacute;ltimo recurso. Em caso de disputas, tente resolver primeiro com o suporte. Se o problema n&atilde;o puder ser resolvido, voc&ecirc; pode solicitar uma indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o. O uso indevido ou solicita&ccedil;&otilde;es maliciosas resultar&atilde;o na rejei&ccedil;&atilde;o permanente de futuras indeniza&ccedil;&otilde;es.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">2. Tipos de Indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A garantia b&aacute;sica cobre os seguintes casos (A falha da solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o ser&aacute; considerada uma solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o maliciosa. A fun&ccedil;&atilde;o de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o ser&aacute; suspensa por 7 dias na primeira falha. Se a falha ocorrer duas vezes consecutivas, a fun&ccedil;&atilde;o ser&aacute; permanentemente suspensa):</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(1) Viola&ccedil;&atilde;o sem reembolso:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Se, nos &uacute;ltimos 30 dias, voc&ecirc; tiver cometido qualquer viola&ccedil;&atilde;o, como: hedging, explora&ccedil;&atilde;o de bugs, martingale, ou uso de scripts, a plataforma dever&aacute; devolver o valor principal do seu dep&oacute;sito. Caso seu saque tenha sido rejeitado ou voc&ecirc; tenha sido inclu&iacute;do na lista negra, voc&ecirc; deve primeiro tentar resolver o problema com o suporte da plataforma. Somente se a negocia&ccedil;&atilde;o falhar, voc&ecirc; poder&aacute; solicitar indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o. Tenha certeza que n&atilde;o h&aacute; nenhuma tarefa de aposta pendente (sem volume de apostas ou requisitos de apostas, exceto auditorias do sistema) ao enviar uma solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o. O valor da indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o pode exceder o valor do seu dep&oacute;sito inicial. Ap&oacute;s o sucesso da indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o, sua conta ser&aacute; automaticamente inclu&iacute;da na lista negra e n&atilde;o poder&aacute; mais ser usada.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #333333; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Observa&ccedil;&otilde;es importantes:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">① Altera&ccedil;&atilde;o do status da conta</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ap&oacute;s o envio da solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o, o status da conta ser&aacute; alterado para \"Em processo de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o\" e o uso ser&aacute; suspenso.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">② Taxa de servi&ccedil;o:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Se a indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o for bem-sucedida, a plataforma cobrar&aacute; uma taxa de 3%.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(2) Pagamentos manuais falsos:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Se, nos &uacute;ltimos 30 dias, voc&ecirc; tiver realizado um saque manual com sucesso, mas o valor n&atilde;o foi creditado em sua conta; voc&ecirc; deve, primeiro, tentar resolver o problema com o suporte. Somente se a negocia&ccedil;&atilde;o falhar, voc&ecirc; poder&aacute; solicitar indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o. O valor da indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o n&atilde;o pode exceder o valor do pagamento falso e sua conta n&atilde;o deve ter nenhuma tarefa de aposta pendente (sem volume de apostas ou requisitos de apostas, exceto auditorias do sistema). Ap&oacute;s a indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o bem-sucedida, a conta poder&aacute; ser usada normalmente.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">3. Per&iacute;odo de envio e validade</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(1) Site ativo:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Se o site est&aacute; em opera&ccedil;&atilde;o normal, solicite atrav&eacute;s de \"Perfil\" &gt; \"Garantia e Indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o de Terceiros\". S&oacute; ser&atilde;o aceitas solicita&ccedil;&otilde;es no per&iacute;odo de 30 dias da disputa.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(2) Site encerrado: </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Se o site estiver permanentemente fechado, a indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o pode ser solicitada no site oficial da NO Wallet.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(3) Prazo de validade:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> As solicita&ccedil;&otilde;es devem ser feita dentro de 30 dias da disputa, caso contr&aacute;rio, n&atilde;o ser&atilde;o aceitas. Disputas ocorridas antes do site participar do servi&ccedil;o de garantia n&atilde;o est&atilde;o inclu&iacute;das no escopo da indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">4. Processo de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(1) Pr&eacute;-requisito:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Solicita&ccedil;&otilde;es de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o s&oacute; podem ser feitas ap&oacute;s negocia&ccedil;&otilde;es sem sucesso com o suporte.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(2) Processo e prazo:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ap&oacute;s enviar a solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o, a NO Wallet revisar&aacute; a solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o e os documentos de suporte (1-7 dias &uacute;teis) e decidir&aacute; o resultado da indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o. Durante esse per&iacute;odo, a conta ser&aacute; suspensa.</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">5. M&eacute;todo de Verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(1) Endere&ccedil;o &uacute;nico: </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">A NO Wallet possui um mecanismo exclusivo de garantia e indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o, que s&oacute; pode ser verificado no site oficial </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(</span><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://no.com\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #1155cc; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">no.com</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> ou</span><a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.no.com\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #1155cc; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">www.no.com</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">. Ap&oacute;s verificar que a plataforma aderiu ao servi&ccedil;o de garantia da NO Wallet, voc&ecirc; pode enviar uma solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o de indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(2) Base para a indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> Somente o endere&ccedil;o do site pode ser usado para verificar e confirmar se o site est&aacute; dentro do escopo da garantia da NO Wallet. O endere&ccedil;o do site &eacute; a &uacute;nica base para a indeniza&ccedil;&atilde;o.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">(3) Processo de verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Verdana,sans-serif; color: #666666; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Digite manualmente o endere&ccedil;o do site oficial da NO Wallet para evitar clicar em links ou colar poss&iacute;veis URLs falsos. Preencha o endere&ccedil;o do site na caixa de pesquisa e verifique se o servi&ccedil;o de garantia foi ativado.</span><span style=\"font-size: